ython SDK Module (`python-sdk/`)\n\n**Location:** `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/python-sdk/`\n\n**Package layout:**\n```\npython-sdk/\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ pyproject.toml                          # Package: agentcube-sdk, Python >=3.10\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ design.md                               # SDK design reference doc\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ spec.md                                 # SDK specification\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ agentcube/\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ __init__.py                         # Public exports: CodeInterpreterClient, AgentRuntimeClient\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ agent_runtime.py                    # AgentRuntimeClient (IMPLEMENTED)\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ code_interpreter.py                 # CodeInterpreterClient (IMPLEMENTED)\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ exceptions.py                       # Exception hierarchy\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ clients/\nв”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ __init__.py                     # Re-exports: ControlPlaneClient, CodeInterpreterDataPlaneClient, AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient\nв”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ control_plane.py                # ControlPlaneClient\nв”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ code_interpreter_data_plane.py  # CodeInterpreterDataPlaneClient\nв”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ agent_runtime_data_plane.py     # AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient (IMPLEMENTED)\nв”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ utils/\nв”Ӯ       в”ңв”Җв”Җ __init__.py                     # Empty module marker\nв”Ӯ       в”ңв”Җв”Җ http.py                         # create_session()\nв”Ӯ       в”ңв”Җв”Җ log.py                          # get_logger()\nв”Ӯ       в””в”Җв”Җ utils.py                        # read_token_from_file()\nв””в”Җв”Җ tests/\n    в”ңв”Җв”Җ __init__.py\n    в”ңв”Җв”Җ conftest.py                         # pytest fixtures\n    в”ңв”Җв”Җ test_imports.py                     # Import/export tests\n    в”ңв”Җв”Җ test_utils.py                       # Utility function tests\n    в””в”Җв”Җ test_exceptions.py                  # Exception hierarchy tests\n```\n\n**Dependencies** (from `pyproject.toml`):\n```toml\ndependencies = [\"requests\", \"PyJWT>=2.0.0\", \"cryptography\"]\nrequires-python = \">=3.10\"\n```\n\n---\n\n### 3. Existing AgentRuntimeClient Implementation\n\n**File:** `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/python-sdk/agentcube/agent_runtime.py`\n\nThe `AgentRuntimeClient` is **already fully implemented** (79 lines):\n\n```python\nclass AgentRuntimeClient:\n    \"\"\"High-level client for Agent Runtime invocation.\n\n    Bootstraps sessions and invokes agent workloads through the Router.\n    \"\"\"\n\n    def __init__(\n        self,\n        agent_name: str,\n        namespace: str = \"default\",\n        router_url: Optional[str] = None,\n        verbose: bool = False,\n        session_id: Optional[str] = None,\n        timeout: int = 120,\n        connect_timeout: float = 5.0,\n    ):\n        # ... resolves router_url from arg or ROUTER_URL env\n        # ... creates AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient\n        # ... bootstraps session_id if not provided\n\n    def __enter__(self) -> \"AgentRuntimeClient\": ...\n    def __exit__(self, exc_type, exc_val, exc_tb) -> None: ...\n    def invoke(self, payload: Dict[str, Any], timeout: Optional[float] = None) -> Any:\n        # validates session_id, delegates to dp_client.invoke(), returns resp.json()\n    def close(self) -> None:\n        # dp_client.close()\n```\n\n**File:** `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/python-sdk/agentcube/clients/agent_runtime_data_plane.py`\n\nThe `AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient` is **already fully implemented** (80 lines):\n\n```python\nclass AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient:\n    SESSION_HEADER = \"x-agentcube-session-id\"\n\n    def __init__(self, router_url, namespace, agent_name, timeout=120, connect_timeout=5.0, pool_connections=10, pool_maxsize=10):\n        # base_url = urljoin(router_url, f\"/v1/namespaces/{namespace}/agent-runtimes/{agent_name}/invocations/\")\n        # session = create_session(...)\n\n    def bootstrap_session_id(self) -> str:\n        # GET self.base_url, read x-agentcube-session-id header\n\n    def invoke(self, session_id, payload, timeout=None) -> requests.Response:\n        # POST self.base_url with session header + JSON body\n\n    def close(self) -> None:\n        # session.close()\n```\n\n---\n\n### 4. Existing tasks.md and Planning Documents\n\n**Root-level tasks.md:** `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/tasks.md`\n- This is for **AR-023** (CLI invoke/status commands), NOT AR-028.\n- Contains 15 detailed tasks (T-1 through T-15) with dependency graphs and parallelizable groups.\n\n**AR-028 tasks.md:** `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-028/tasks.md`\n- **This file is a skeleton/placeholder** -- all content is TODO comments.\n- States: \"Precondition: Stage ST-3 (Design) completed\"\n- References: `changes/AR-028/proposal.md`, `changes/AR-028/design.md`, `changes/AR-028/delta-spec.md`\n\n**AR-027 tasks.md** (predecessor, fully populated): `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-027/tasks.md`\n- Contains 15 detailed tasks (T-1 through T-15) with full implementation steps, verification commands, dependency graphs, and acceptance criteria. This is the **pattern to follow** for AR-028.\n\n---\n\n### 5. SDK Client Pattern (Base Classes, HTTP Transport, etc.)\n\nThe SDK uses a **two-layer facade pattern**:\n\n**Layer 1: Public Client (Facade)** -- e.g., `CodeInterpreterClient`, `AgentRuntimeClient`\n- Handles configuration resolution (args + env vars)\n- Manages session lifecycle (create/bootstrap/reuse)\n- Implements context manager protocol (`__enter__`/`__exit__`)\n- Delegates to data plane/control plane clients\n- Provides high-level methods\n\n**Layer 2: Internal Clients** -- e.g., `ControlPlaneClient`, `CodeInterpreterDataPlaneClient`, `AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient`\n- Raw HTTP operations via `requests.Session`\n- Connection pooling via `HTTPAdapter(pool_connections=10, pool_maxsize=10)`\n- Base URL construction via `urljoin()`\n- Timeout tuples: `(connect_timeout, read_timeout)` -- defaults `(5.0, 120)`\n\n**Shared utilities:**\n- `create_session()` -- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/python-sdk/agentcube/utils/http.py`\n- `get_logger()` -- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/python-sdk/agentcube/utils/log.py`\n- `read_token_from_file()` -- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/python-sdk/agentcube/utils/utils.py`\n\n**Exception hierarchy** (`/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/python-sdk/agentcube/exceptions.py`):\n```python\nclass AgentCubeError(Exception): pass\nclass CommandExecutionError(AgentCubeError): ...  # exit_code, stderr, command\nclass SessionError(AgentCubeError): pass\nclass DataPlaneError(AgentCubeError): pass\n```\n\n**Session header convention:** `x-agentcube-session-id` (lowercase), set as default header on the `requests.Session` object or explicitly per-request.\n\n---\n\n### 6. ST-3 Stage Completion Artifacts and Design Docs\n\n**ST-3 (Design) is completed for AR-028.** The evidence:\n\n1. **Root-level `design.md`** (`/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/design.md`) -- **Fully populated** (449 lines). Contains:\n   - Architecture diagram (Public Client -> Data Plane Client -> HTTP Utilities)\n   - Data structures (AgentRuntimeClient fields, AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient fields, exception hierarchy)\n   - API contracts (full method signatures, configuration resolution table, lifecycle steps)\n   - Error handling (exception flow, error scenarios table, timeout behavior)\n   - Testing strategy (test categories, key test scenarios table, mocking strategy)\n   - Usage examples (3 code examples)\n\n2. **Root-level `proposal.md`** (`/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/proposal.md`) -- **Fully populated** (319 lines). Contains:\n   - Purpose (in Chinese), scope (in/out), impact analysis, risk assessment\n   - 5 alternatives considered with decisions\n   - Implementation notes with code skeletons\n   - Acceptance criteria checklist\n\n3. **Root-level `delta-spec.md`** does NOT cover AR-028 -- it covers AR-026 (K8s/AgentCube Provider).\n\n4. **`changes/AR-028/delta-spec.md`** (`/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-028/delta-spec.md`) -- **Fully populated** (228 lines). Contains:\n   - Detailed Gherkin-style requirements for AgentRuntimeClient and AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient\n   - File changes table\n\n5. **`changes/AR-028/design.md`** -- **Empty skeleton** (41 lines, all TODO comments).\n\n6. **`changes/AR-028/proposal.md`** -- **Empty skeleton** (33 lines, all TODO comments).\n\n**Key observation:** The fully populated design/proposal docs are at the **root level** (`/design.md`, `/proposal.md`), while the `changes/AR-028/` directory contains only the completed `delta-spec.md` and skeleton `design.md`/`proposal.md`/`tasks.md`.\n\n---\n\n### 7. AR-028 References Across the Codebase\n\nAR-028 is referenced in **8 files**:\n\n| File | Description |\n|------|-------------|\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/design.md` | Full AR-028 design document (449 lines) |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/proposal.md` | Full AR-028 proposal (319 lines, Chinese) |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/.sdd_prompt.md` | SDD prompt containing AR-028 specs as context |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn